==English==
===Tag===
'''[[do]]/[[does]]''' ''one'''''?'''<BR>
'''does [[one]]?'''

# ''Request for confirmation that converts a negative present tense sentence into a question. Expects agreement in a "no" answer.''
#:''You don't expect me to go in there, '''do you'''?''

====Usage notes====
As a tag, always used with an object pronoun substituting for the subject. Plurality agrees with ''do'' or ''does''.

